=Write a professional project proposal for:

CLIENT: {{ $json.clientName }}
COMPANY: {{ $json.clientCompany }}
SERVICE: {{ $json.service }}

REQUIREMENTS:
{{ $json.requirements }}

PRICING:
- Base Price: ${{ $json.basePrice }}
- Add-ons: {{ JSON.stringify($json.addons) }}
- Total: ${{ $json.totalPrice }}
- Payment Terms: 50% advance (${{ $json.advancePayment }}), 50% on delivery

TIMELINE: {{ $json.timeline || '10 business days' }}

Write the following sections:
1. Executive Summary (2-3 sentences)
2. Project Scope (bullet points)
3. Our Process (4 steps: Discovery, Design, Development, Launch)
4. Investment Breakdown (line items)
5. Timeline (phases with dates)
6. Next Steps

Keep it professional but friendly. Highlight AI advantages (speed, quality, cost). Make it persuasive.
